Title: Words and Deeds
Plot: House splits his time between treating a firefighter for uncontrollable shivering, giving Tritter a piece of his mind, and handling his trial for forging prescriptions.
GuestStars: Jason George, Hira Ambrosino, Aulani Rhea, Terryn Westbrook, Tory Kittles, Martin Mullen, Brian Leckner, David Morse, Meagan Good, Vyto Ruginis, Helen Carey, Kadeem Hardison, Donald Sage MacKay
